ACT_ADMIN --> UC_RPT_01
ACT_ADMIN --> UC_RPT_02
ACT_ADMIN --> UC_RPT_03
ACT_ADMIN --> UC_RPT_04
ACT_ADMIN --> UC_RPT_05

note right of SYS_RPT
  derived from source code
  Primary source:
  - ReportController.java
  Supporting sources:
  - frontend/src/hooks/use-dashboard-data.ts
